<plot>Jean and Maryann are friends, maybe even best friends. They belong to the same ladies' group. They confide in one another, build each other up and share an ever-growing Christian faith. After a lovely afternoon of fellowship, Maryann reveals her concerns about her non-believing boyfriend, Michael, to Jean. Jean feels a desire to do what she believes is best for Maryann. Are these the desires of a loving friend or something more? How far will Jean go and what will the repercussions be?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?652631</url></doc>
